1948;;Esther Waters;;British;;Ian Dalrymple;;Kathleen Ryan, Dirk Bogarde;;historical drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esther_Waters_(film);;The film is set in London in 1875.Esther (Kathleen Ryan) goes into domestic service as a maid, only to be seduced by sweet-talking footman William (Dirk Bogarde). When he abandons her, she must deal with not only pregnancy but also her mother's death. She struggles to survive with only herself for comfort and strength.She is forced to put her child into care in order to keep her job.